        "description": "Champions, Version 1.3 is available now with two-handed weapons, smooth turning, and localization/subtitles.\n-----\nUntil You Fall is an arcade-inspired, hack-and-slash roguelite where you can define and master your own fighting style for hours of frantic, kinetic fun.\n\nPrepare for the fight of your life. Move your arms and body to the synthwave soundtrack as you attack, block, cast spells, and dodge your way deeper into a neon fantasy world filled with magic-infused monsters. Equip yourself with a variety of gameplay-altering, one- and two-handed weapons as you continue to gain strength and strike down the monstrosities that lurk throughout this mystifying world.\n\nFeatures\n+ Runs that include randomized rewards, powerups, enemy configurations, and rooms; no two runs are quite the same\n+ Driving synthwave soundtrack that keeps you moving in and out of the game\n+ Customizable comfort and accessibility options to help you move and battle with ease\n\nJoin our community on Discord.",
